Recently, an article published by the New York Times said that a record number of immigrant children were entering the United States unaccompanied by their parents. Many of them would engage in jobs that violate the laws of child labor. Besides, according to the U.S. Department of Labor, the number of children employed illegally by companies across the U.S. has increased by 69 percent since 2018. Please tell us your views on the illegal employment of child labor in the United States.